PrecisAppointment of JOHANNE BÉLISLE of Montréal, Quebec, to be Commissioner of Patents, to hold office during pleasure for a term of five years; and appointment of JOHANNE BÉLISLE to be Registrar of Trade-marks, to hold office during pleasure for a term of five years, effective September 8, 2015.
